data.description: Brand new construction underway with character and charm built by a pre-eminent coastal builder. Urban Infill is proud to announce Old Gulf Cottages with a beginning price point of $169,900 on 4 different plans (1 ADA compliant) with options (30 lots available). Incredible location; walk to Big Lagoon Park (trails, boat launch on Intracoastal waterway), county park (tennis courts, basketball, playground, pavilion), the library, and Wolf Bay Lodge restaurant. Just minutes to Publix, the Naval Air Station, and the white sand beaches of Perdido Key. Standard features include: granite/quartz counters in kitchen, 9' ceilings for one-story homes (10' ground floor for two-story), Frigidaire stainless appliance selection, cement board siding, 14 SEER HVAC, all wood cabinets with crown on uppers... unparalleled value within Hellen Caro elementary district and flood insurance not required. Late June completion.
